      <title>大堡礁濒临灭绝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/great-barrier-reef-teeters-on-the-brink-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最新研究，澳大利亚大堡礁周围的水温是过去 400 年来最高的。这一发现进一步证实了人类引发的气候变化正在将大堡礁推向临界点的可能性，它可能无法恢复。保罗·艾伦 (Paul Allen) 报道更多详情。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/great-barrier-reef-teeters-on-the-brink-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:13:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔莫蒂表示瑞银有望实现 2026 年目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/ermotti-says-ubs-is-on-track-to-deliver-2026-targets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂 (Sergio Ermotti) 在公布第二季度高于预期的利润后讨论了该银行的业绩和前景，支持向股东返还资本并完成瑞信整合的努力。他在苏黎世与弗朗辛·拉夸进行了交谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/ermotti-says-ubs-is-on-track-to-deliver-2026-targets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国通胀率涨幅低于预期，服务业降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/uk-inflation-rises-less-than-expected-with-a-cooling-in-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通胀率今年首次回升，但仍低于经济学家和英国央行预期的水平，这增强了进一步放松利率的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/uk-inflation-rises-less-than-expected-with-a-cooling-in-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:05:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着欧洲电气化，EON 加大电网支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/eon-boosts-spending-on-energy-transition-as-europe-electrifies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着德国公用事业公司 EON SE 扩建庞大的电缆网络以推动能源转型，该公司上半年的投资增加了 20% 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/eon-boosts-spending-on-energy-transition-as-europe-electrifies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 05:00:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银利润超出预期，财富流入达到 270 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/ubs-profit-beats-estimates-as-client-inflows-hit-27-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团第二季度利润高于预期，强劲的客户流入和投资银行收入帮助首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂 (Sergio Ermotti) 向股东返还资本的努力得到了支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/ubs-profit-beats-estimates-as-client-inflows-hit-27-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国贷款下降引发“资产负债表”衰退担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-s-rare-loan-drop-stokes-fears-of-balance-sheet-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国近二十年来首次缩减银行贷款，引发人们担忧中国这一全球第二大经济体正像日本几十年前那样陷入“资产负债表衰退”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-s-rare-loan-drop-stokes-fears-of-balance-sheet-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国交易商溢价购买债券以规避监管限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/china-traders-pay-premium-for-bonds-to-avoid-regulatory-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，中国交易员正在以溢价购买国债，以逃避监管机构对前所未有的股市上涨的控制。]]></description>
